The Zondo Commission will continue to hear Transnet related testimony from the Executive Manager in the Finance Department of Transnet Freight Rail: Yousuf Laher * Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. JOHANNESBURG - The state capture inquiry will continue hearing Transnet-related testimony on Wednesday. The company's finance manager, Yousuf Laher, will be appearing at the commission. On Tuesday, former Rail for Hatch director, Henk Bester, told the commission he got a call from two people demanding to be included in a rail project.